0.49-98
	* use 4glpc.hlp not 4glpc.iem for help messages
	* lib/libaubit4gl/stack.c, lib/libsql/esqlc/esql.ec,
	  tools/adbschema/makefile, tools/adbschema/table.4gl: Add some
	  basic blob handling, add fragments to adbschema
	* compilers/sql/80.reqd: Fix bug in SELECT .. FOR UPDATE
	* lib/libui/ui_curses/iarray.c: MID  0000614 - make it so it only
	  goes down 1 row when paging down to insert a new row...
	* lib/libsql/odbc/sql.c: Fixup for a mantis issue 722 -
	  SQL_ATTR_CURSOR_TYPE
	* tools/asql/: execute.4gl, paginate.4gl, runforms/makefile: Make
	  file cleanup & variable renaming
	* lib/libui/ui_highlevel/: formcntrl.c, lowlevel/widget_gtk.c:
	  int_driver rename & comment removal
	* lib/liblex/lex_esqlc/compile_c.c: Small comment cleanup
	* lib/libaubit4gl/: .splintrc, a4gl_libaubit4gl_int.h,
	  attributes.c, builtin.c, builtin_d.c, match.c, stack.c: lint
	  fixups
	* lib/bin/dlmagic: Small fixups
	* incl/a4gl_sql.h: Add extra generic field to s_sid
	* etc/import/README: Tidy import naming convention
	* compilers/4glc/: mk_states_c.in, rules/main.rule: Small fixups -
	  change // comments to /* in mk_states.c	      remove a
	  reduce/reduce error in main.rule
	* etc/convertsql/INFORMIX-POSTGRES.cnv: Change mapping of SET
	  ISOLATION commands
	* compilers/sql/: 80.reqd, util.c: Fix invalid 'free' reported by
	  Leonardo Cecchi

